						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Right face of a fragment of stone lying in the compound of Śaṅkaraliṅga temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th Century A.D.,</hi> registers a gift of land and house-site to Barmayya, by Sōmayya, devotee of Kōṭiśaṁkaradēva, for the maintenance of a charity picotta.</p>						

